ISLAMABAD, Dec 17 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi on Tuesday summoned a session of the National Assembly on Tuesday in the Parliament House.
The president summoned the session to meet on December 20 at 5:30pm under the powers conferred by Clause (1) Article 54 of the Constitution of Pakistan, President Secretariat Press Wing said in a press release.
